Common.Strapline.Common.Text: LONG TERM LEASE - PREMIUM GOVERNMENT COVENANT

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Deadline Private Sale closing Thursday 31st August 2017 at 3pm.

Located only meters from Nunawading's prestigious Golden Mile retail strip, this hi-tech office warehouse is surrounded by amenity.

The property has immediate access to public transport with bus routes along Whitehorse Road connecting to Nunawading and Blackburn railway stations. Access to the Eastern Freeway (connecting with EastLink) is only two kilometres* away; connectivity to the CBD, Port of Melbourne and South East suburbs is easy.

Surrounding national tenants include Bunnings, Brand Smart Outlet Centre, Nick Scali Furniture and Officeworks among others.

Property features include:
- Positioned on its own title
- Land parcel: 1,041sqm*
- Corporate two level office: 374sqm*
- Clearspan warehouse: 484sqm*
- Total building area: 858 sqm
- 210m* from Golden Mile
- Fibre internet connection
- Amenities on both levels
- Full height container roller doors
- 40ft container access

*approx.
